Titolo: Typhoon Thompson

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Typhoon Thompson in Search for the Sea Child is a 1988 computer game created by Dan Gorlin.  It was published by Broderbund for the Atari ST and later for Amiga (1990). Typhoon Thompson is a remake of the Apple II game from Broderbund called Airheart, also written by Gorlin.